nodes.text: Warriors of Endor was an article written by Ally Wybrew. It discussed the heroics, weapons, trivia, allies, and enemies of five notable Ewoks of Endor. Detailed in the article were Wicket, Paploo, Chukha-Trok, Logray, and Deej Warrick. The article was published in Star Wars Insider 110 and later reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2013.
